### 1. Global Helpers & Authentication

#### [MODIFY] [auth.js](file:///c:/Users/user/Documents/AI%20Vitta%202026/js/auth.js)
- Tambahkan helper global `window.getScopedKey(baseKey)` di dalam `js/auth.js` agar bisa diakses di semua halaman.
```javascript
window.getScopedKey = function(baseKey) {
    const activeDept = window.getActiveDept ? window.getActiveDept() : null;
    if (activeDept && activeDept.id) {
        return activeDept.id + '_' + baseKey;
    }
    return baseKey;
};
```

